md:
giải nghĩa từ "dental" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan và các từ trái nghĩa.

* Dental (adjective): relating to the teeth or dentistry
	+ Meaning in Vietnamese: liên quan đến răng hoặc nha khoa
	+ Example sentence: The dental clinic provides a wide range of services, including teeth whitening and orthodontics.
	+ Related words: dentist, dental care, dental hygiene, tooth
	+ Antonyms: medical, surgical

* Dental (noun): a dental clinic or office
	+ Meaning in Vietnamese: phòng khám răng hoặc văn phòng nha khoa
	+ Example sentence: I have an appointment at the dental tomorrow morning.
	+ Related words: dentist, dental care, dental hygiene, tooth
	+ Antonyms: medical clinic, hospital

Note: The word "dental" can have different meanings depending on the context in which it is used. In the first definition, it is an adjective describing something related to teeth or dentistry, while in the second definition, it is a noun referring to a dental clinic or office.
